It is my impression that the one thing lacking in coverage of cannabis equities has been objectivity (This happens frequently with emerging industries) There are simply too many management promoters (e.g. $TLRY) and too many conflicted and bullish commentators. One of the

exceptions is Alan Brochstein @Invest420 who I have found to be an excellent, informative and non biased source. If you are a serious investor and want no nonsense and objective analysis I would subscribe to his 420Investor.com and
